Game APP Data model design


1. APP Features
1) Register
	player:
		name:
		mobile telephone:
		email:
		sex:male/female
2) Log in 
	mobile phone:
	password or verification code:
3) Buy bonus: 
	room card:10 rmb --> 20 rounds

4) Enter room - 4 digit numbers(e.g. 5122)
5) ...


2. Playing data exchange
1) room:
	type:ROOM	
	rid:0-~
	status: "WAITING"
	gameRound:
	betRound:
	defendseat:
	focuses:[0,0,..,0]
	players: ["aa","bb",...,"ii"]
	balances: [0,0,...,0]
	checkcards: [false, ...,false]
	discards: [true,...,true]
	reserve: "TBD"
	
2) player:
	type:PLAYER
	rid:	0
	pid:0
	msgType:	JOIN/LEFT/WAITING/PLAYING
	name:"aa"
	gameRound:
	betRound:
	seatID:0
	seatDID:0
	focus:false
	checkcard:false
	discard:false
	betvol:0
	balance:0
	robot:false
	reserve:"TBD"

3) cards:
	type:CARDS	
	cardsName:jh
	rid:	0
	gameRound:0
	points: 0-12
	suits: 0-3
	cardsTypes: "Higcard", "Pair",...
	reserve: "TBD"
4) The props(道具)